parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
or stays on steadily; the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag light can indicate a malfunctioning airbag system, which can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of an accident, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag does not deploy in the event of an accident
despite the vehicle being involved in a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Acceleration and Sticky Accelerator Pedal
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration and sticky accelerator pedal can cause the vehicle to lurch forward, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal sticks or feels soft
the pedal does not return to its normal position
or the vehicle lurches forward when the pedal is pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause the vehicle to accelerate suddenly, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The cruise control system does not disengage when the brakes are applied

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The ABS system does not function properly
or the vehicle does not slow down when the brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fluctuations in engine RPM can cause the vehicle to lurch forward or lose power, leading to accidents or loss of control.
The corrosion and failure of the subframe can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
causing the wheel to detach or the vehicle to become undrivable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: or the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the vehicle's body can cause structural damage, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle has rust or corrosion on the body
or the cargo carrier slides out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hose can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can result in accidents or injuries.
The failure of the master cylinder can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can result in accidents or injuries.
The failure of the ABS system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to a loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: unusual noises or vibrations when braking

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive wear on brake pads and rotors can cause a loss of braking ability, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Unusual noises or vibrations when braking
excessive dust or debris from the brakes

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A brake fluid leak can cause a loss of braking ability, leading to accidents or injuries.
The engine stalling and failure can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when the vehicle stalls while driving at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: makes loud rattling or grinding sounds

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The oil pan gasket failure can cause oil leaks, engine damage, and accidents due to loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cruise Control and Throttle Body Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cruise control and throttle body failure can cause unintended acceleration, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal sticks to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to honor recalls and warranties can lead to financial losses and safety risks for consumers.
symptoms: The manufacturer refuses to repair or replace defective parts
